pm</li>\r\n 	<li>Precor fitness facility open 24 hours</li>\r\n 	<li>Free parking</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Hotel Events</h3>\r\nCome join us for all the fun!\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/friday-night-events/\">Friday Night Events</a>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/mouse_meet_info_item/room-window-decorating-contest/\">Window Decorating Rules</a>\r\n<h3>About the Hotel</h3>\r\nThere are now so many of our Event Guests that stay at this Hotel that over the years we have built up the Friday evening events to be a fantastic way to kick off the PNWMM Weekend, meet other Guests and have a whole lot of fun!\r\n\r\n​From Interactive Games, Room Window Decorating Contests, Interactive Trivia Games and other added benefits... Embassy Suites is THE place to stay with free parking and is located less than 1 mile from the Lynnwood Convention Center!\r\n\r\n​NOTE: The Embassy Suites recently renovated the entire hotel with all new refreshed rooms,\r\n\r\natrium, seating area, restaurant, meetings space and more.\r\n\r\n​We have negotiated fantastic Group Room Rates that include the following for Guests booking at this hotel:​\r\n\r\nFree Wi-Fi; Children under 18 no additional cost; Free Hot Breakfast each morning of your stay; Every room is a Suite; Free Admission to the PNWMM Friday Night Events including games, activities, Trivia Contest, music and more; and ability to participate in the very popular Hotel Room Window Decorating Contest.','PNWMM Partner Hotel | Embassy Suites Lynnwood','','publish','closed','closed','','embassy-suites-hotel','','','2022-03-23 21:20:28','2022-03-23 21:20:28','',0,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/?post_type=locations&#038;p=220',0,'locations','',0),(221,1,'2018-10-22 03:54:15','2018-10-22 03:54:15','','embassy','','inherit','open','closed','','embassy','','','2018-10-22 03:54:15','2018-10-22 03:54:15','',220,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/embassy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(222,1,'2018-10-22 03:55