e Lynnwood Convention Center and has grown from 150 Guests to over 400 Guests today.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Our PNW Mouse Meet Team:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\r\n<div>\r\n<img src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/cf0bfea9f2c56fbbe32846cf6e6dd886.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"223\" height=\"242\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-428\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Don Morin</h3>\r\n<h4>Founder/Host</h4>\r\nSince 2009 Don and his team have been creating a magical experience for so many Guests.\r\n\"Passion, Disney Fandom and giving them more than they expect are key ingredients to our success!\"\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex-container\">\r\n<div>\r\n<img src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1eb0bf4be885c7332a88b09abc007fb8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"214\" height=\"186\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-429\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>PNW Mouse Meet Volunteer Team</h3>\r\n<h4>Founder/Host</h4>\r\nSince 2009 Don and his team have been creating a magical experience for so many Guests.\r\n\"Passion, Disney Fandom and giving them more than they expect are key ingredients to our success!\"\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','161-revision-v1','','','2019-01-27 19:13:13','2019-01-27 19:13:13','',161,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/161-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(431,1,'2019-01-27 19:14:52','2019-01-27 19:14:52','<div id=\"wsb-element-3bb85533-e9db-4d83-9dc8-47bff2cd65d0\" class=\"wsb-element-text\" data-type=\"element\">\r\n<div class=\"txt \">\r\n<h2>Our mission</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"wsb-element-399ae084-d95e-4a76-9412-0b5ec4b163fd\" class=\"wsb-element-text\" data-type=\"element\">\r\n<div class=\"txt \">\r\n\r\nPacific Northwest Mouse Meet™, the premier unofficial Disney® Fan event in America, is committed to quality and excellence in our product, guest experience, people, philanthropy and strategic partners. We are dedicated to communicating, s