iv class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/James2.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/news.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/James.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-912\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/awards.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-913\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/chat.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; width: 100%;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-916\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/mickey.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>','At Work With Walt:  Disney Legend James Algar’s 43 years with Bambi, Lions and Mr. Lincoln.','','inherit','closed','closed','','907-autosave-v1','','','2019-09-10 03:50:06','2019-09-10 03:50:06','',907,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/907-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(922,1,'2020-01-16 04:08:14','2020-01-16 04:08:14','<h3>When to Arrive and Timing of Events</h3>\r\nCheck in begins at 9am. Rope Drop takes place at 10am and our first Guest Speaker begins at 11am. Be sure to arrive early and don’t miss a thing!\r\nDO bring your ID as this is how we will check you in. Bring a smile, camera and a pocket full of Pixie Dust… We will do the rest!\r\n<h3>Food, Snacks, and More!</h3>\r\nThe Lynnwood Convention Center will have three food locations serving Sandwiches, Salads, Pizza, Ice Cream, Popcorn, Mickey Rice Krispy Treats, Coffee, Sodas and so much more. They will even have Mint Juleps with or without a splash of Bourbon! Vegetarian Food options will be available.\r\n<h3>PNWMM Info Booth</h3>\r\nHere you can ask any questions about the event as well as purchase exclusive Limited Edition PNWMM Pins (new design this year!!), a new PNWMM Print, logo shirts, mugs, pens and more!\r\n<a name=\"guest\"></a><a name=\"celebrity\"></a>\r\n<h3>Celebrity Meet &amp; Greets</h3>\r\nAll of our Guest Speakers will be available at various times to meet YOU! Because of high Guest demand to meet Guest Speakers we do have to limit time and items to be signed so that as many Guests can meet them as possible. There may be a charge to meet the Guest Speakers or for Autographs. More details will be confirmed as we get closer to the event date.\r\n\r\nWe ask for your understanding and cooperation so that as many Guests as possible can meet our Guest Speakers. Thank you.\r\n\r\n<a name=\"photo\"></a>\r\n<h3>PNW Mouse Meet Photo Stops</h3>\r\nBe sure to keep an eye out for PNW Mouse Meet Photo Stops all around the Event space! From amazing one of a kind displays and homages to Disney Park Icons to Disney Park Attractions Vehicles, there will be many unique ways to take that special photo!\r\n<h3>  Fan Displays and Photo Opps</h3>\r\nWe will have several amazing Fan created displays for your enjoyment! We have once again worked very hard to Plus Up several displays and to create new and exciting photo opportunities to make magical memories.\r\n<a name=\"raffle\"></a>\r\n<h3>Raffle for Charity</h3>\r\nWe again this year have put together a number of AMAZING Prize baskets… themed to Mickey Mouse, Walt Disney Imagineering, Club 33, Signed book collections, a Dooney &amp; Bourke bag, luggage and so many other great things. Again this year we will be supporting the Ryman Arts which was founded by Disney Legend Marty Sklar in honor of Disney Legend Herb Ryman, helping underprivileged kids expand on their art skills, stay in school and go on to college and careers. The other benefactor of our Charity dollars is Seattle Childrens Hospital. We are proud to support both\r\nof these fine charities. The Raffle Tickets are Cash Only so please be sure to bring enough to support your needs for Tickets. There is NO ATM on premise and there nearest bank is a couple of blocks away. You are going to LOVE these charity raffle prizes!!\r\n<a name=\"disneyana\"></a>\r\n<h3>Disneyana Vendors</h3>\r\nWe are excited for the variety of Vendors this year… some new and some past favorites! Authors, Art, Jewelry, Custom Ears, Ornaments and so much more! Some Vendors only accept cash and others accept credit cards. Be sure to be prepared for both. You can visit our website to see a full list of Vendors at the 2020 PNWMM <a href=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/pnw_mouse_meets/2020/\">here.</a>\r\n\r\n<a name=\"cosplay\"></a>\r\n<h3>Disney-Bounding &amp; Cosplay</h3>\r\nWe LOVE seeing all the amazing costumes, bounding, ears, shoes, hats and so many other creative wearables…\r\n\r\nJust a few rules: Please ensure your costumes and bounding are themed to Disney, safe, no weapons and is in good taste. PNWMM Team has the right to ask that dangerous items or inappropriate costumes be left in vehicles or at home. Guests that don’t follow these and other\r\nrules may be asked to leave.\r\n\r\nYou may be photographed, or video recorded by PNWMM, Media or other Guests. We appreciate the work you put into your outfits and we can’t wait to see what you have created!!\r\n\r\n<a name=\"fans\"></a>\r\n<h3>Opportunity to Meet Other Disney Fans</h3>\r\nOne thing we’ve learned over the past 11 years, is that there have been SO many connections and friendships made at all the PNW Mouse Meet events through the years...One couple even met and got married! So don’t be shy about saying hello to every other Disney Fan you come across at the event...Remember...We ALL have the same thing in common!! So look forward to seeing old friends and meeting new ones as well! And be sure to say hello to our PNWMM Team in the Red Shirts...They work hard so that you can have a Magical Day! And come say hello to me (Don) too! We would love to chat with you!\r\n\r\nWe can\'t wait to meet YOU!\r\n\r\nIf you have other questions please email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@pnwmousemeet.com\">info@pnwmousemeet.com</a>','Know Before You Go','','inherit','closed','closed','','659-revision-v1','','','2020-01-16 04:08:14','2020-01-16 04:08:14','',659,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/659-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(923,1,'2020-01-16 04:10:15','2020-01-16 04:10:15','<div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Vendors will be Announced Soon!</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n<h5>Check Back Soon</h5>\r\nWe are excited for the variety of Vendors this year… some new and some past favorites! Authors, Art, Jewelry, Custom Ears, Ornaments and so much more!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2020 Vendors','','publish','closed','closed','','2020-vendors','','','2020-01-16 04:10:39','2020-01-16 04:10:39','',0,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/?page_id=923',0,'page','',0),(924,1,'2020-01-16 04:10:15','2020-01-16 04:10:15','<div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Vendors will be Announced Soon!</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n<h5>Check Back Soon</h5>\r\nWe are excited for the variety of Vendors this year… some new and some past favorites! Authors, Art, Jewelry, Custom Ears, Ornaments and so much more!','2020 Vendors','','inherit','closed','closed','','923-revision-v1','','','2020-01-16 04:10:15','2020-01-16 04:10:15','',923,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/923-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(925,1,'2020-01-16 04:10:39','2020-01-16 04:10:39','<div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Vendors will be Announced Soon!</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n<h5>Check Back Soon</h5>\r\nWe are excited for the variety of Vendors this year… some new and some past favorites! Authors, Art, Jewelry, Custom Ears, Ornaments and so much more!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2020 Vendors','','inherit','closed','closed','','923-revision-v1','','','2020-01-16 04:10:39','2020-01-16 04:10:39','',923,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/923-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(926,1,'2020-01-16 04:15:11','2020-01-16 04:15:11','<h5>PNW Mouse Meet’s Friday Night Kickoff to the</h5>\r\n<h2>Best Weekend Ever!</h2>\r\n<p class=\"intro\">You know you’ve been waiting for it…. \"The Best Weekend Ever!\"</p>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-1034\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; margin-bottom: 30px;\" src=\"https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/weekend-friday.png\" alt=\"Best Weekend Ever!\" />\r\nJoin us on Friday July 29th for fun games and prizes, activities, and PNW Mouse Meet™ &amp; Disney® themed magic for all. Gather with your PNWMM friends the night before the Main Event at the Embassy Suites Lynnwood to kick off \"The Best Weekend Ever!\"\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"card mouse-meet\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Friday Night Events</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n\r\nYou are sure to have a pixie dusted evening with all the exciting things we have planned for you and so many Disney Fans!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Doors Open 5:30pm to 8:30pm\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Staying at the Hotel: Show your keycard and get in FREE (<a href=\"/locations/embassy-suites-hotel/\">book your room here!</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li>NOT staying at the Hotel: ONLY a $10 admission per person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>Interactive Games: Maximus just might reward you for your aim and accuracy</li>\r\n 	<li>Get your Disney thinking cap on and be prepared to answer some super fun Trivia for prizes only available from Rapunzel’s Tower (PNWMM prize closet). Do you know the answer to tales as old as time?</li>\r\n 	<li>Whether you have a mathematical mind or just enjoy the possibility of winning…. Come prepared to guess the number of treats in the Jar at the Snuggly Duckling.</li>\r\n 	<li>Shop Pins and other Disneyana with Morehouse Collectibles!</li>\r\n 	<li>Mingle with over 100 other PNWMM &amp; Disney Fans!!</li>\r\n 	<li>Participate in or be a spectator of the Amazingly Popular Room Door &amp; Window Decorating Contest!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Body -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Col -->\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"card mouse-meet\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Door Decorating</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n\r\nStaying at the hotel and participating in the window and door decorating contest? We can’t wait to see what you come up with this year. For the rest of us, it’s a must to see all the creativity and talent that goes into these displays.\r\n<h3>Prizes</h3>\r\n<strong>1st Place:</strong>Themed Gift Bag filled with goodies and a $150.00 Disney Gift Card!\r\n<strong>2nd Place:</strong>Themed Gift Bag filled with goodies and a $100.00 Disney Gift Card!\r\n<strong>3rd Place:</strong>Themed Gift Bag with goodies and a $50.00 Disney Gift Card!\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/mouse_meet_info_item/room-window-decorating-contest/\">Door Decorating Information</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/locations/embassy-suites-hotel/\">Hotel Information</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Body -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Col -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Row -->\r\n<div class=\"row intro-paragraph\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h2>Check out Previous Years\' Friday Night Event!</h2>\r\n[smartslider3 slider=11]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n\r\nWhether this is your first time, second or…… maybe even your twelfth... We look forward to getting together with YOU as we get ready for PNW Mouse Meet’s “Best Weekend Ever!”See ya REAL Soon!!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Friday Night Events','','publish','closed','closed','','friday-night-events','','','2022-03-04 15:15:01','2022-03-04 15:15:01','',0,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/?page_id=926',0,'page','',0),(927,1,'2020-01-16 04:15:11','2020-01-16 04:15:11','<h2>Celebration Details Coming Soon!</h2>\r\n<h5>PNW Mouse Meet’s Friday Night Kickoff</h5>\r\n<p class=\"intro\">Join us for fun games and prizes, activities and Disney magic for all. Gather with your PNWMM friends the night before the main event at the Embassy Suites Lynnwood. We will have interactive games, prizes, a photo opp, trivia, surprises and more…</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"card mouse-meet\">\r\n<div class=\"card-header\">\r\n<h3>Door Decorating</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-body\">\r\n\r\nStaying at the hotel and participating in the window and door decorating contest? We can’t wait to see what you come up with this year. For the rest of us, it’s a must to see all the creativity and talent that goes into these displays.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/mouse_meet_info_item/room-window-decorating-contest/\">Door Decorating Information</a>\r\n<h4>Examples from Past Years</h4>\r\n[smartslider3 slider=7]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Body -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Col -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Row -->\r\n<div class=\"row intro-paragraph\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<h2>Check out Previous Years\' Friday Night Event!</h2>\r\n[smartslider3 slider=11]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2020 Friday Night Events','','inherit','closed','closed','','926-revision-v1','','','2020-01-16 04:15:11','2020-01-16 04:15:11','',926,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/926-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(929,1,'2020-01-24 17:06:12','2020-01-24 17:06:12','','rex','','inherit','open','closed','','rex','','','2020-01-24 17:06:12','2020-01-24 17:06:12','',0,'https://pnwmousemeet.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/rex.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(930,1,'2020-01-24 17:06:41','2020-01-24 17:06